WEBVTT

02:35.920 --> 02:36.880
You Chi.

02:41.920 --> 02:42.800
You Chi?

03:01.720 --> 03:04.600
Wu Shiguang, ever since we were kids,

03:05.680 --> 03:07.560
I've been your little tagalong.

03:09.760 --> 03:10.920
I was your playmate.

03:11.880 --> 03:13.240
I left home with you

03:14.760 --> 03:16.480
and braved danger with you.

03:19.320 --> 03:20.920
Why can't I remember it?

03:21.000 --> 03:24.000
I even followed you to the Shilin Sect.

03:24.640 --> 03:26.440
Have you seen Wu Shiguang?

03:26.520 --> 03:28.240
I've got something really fun to tell him.

03:28.320 --> 03:29.640
Master Dragon Deity?

03:29.720 --> 03:32.080
He's busy. Don't bother him.

03:32.160 --> 03:33.920
He's still got a lot to deal with.

03:40.360 --> 03:43.000
The people at the Shilin Sect
are all pretty nice.

03:43.080 --> 03:46.240
You little weasel,
keep that Shilin Sect token on tight.

03:46.320 --> 03:47.920
Or you'll be wiped out.

03:51.080 --> 03:53.360
But the Shilin Sect isn't my home.

03:54.360 --> 03:55.880
A weasel demon like me shouldn't be here.

03:57.760 --> 03:59.520
Is that the Dragon Deity?

03:59.600 --> 04:00.560
-Look.
-He has to be.

04:00.640 --> 04:02.360
Even the demon hunter commander
is standing behind him.

04:02.440 --> 04:04.520
-He has to be.
-That's right.

04:04.600 --> 04:06.720
Exactly, he must be the Dragon Deity!

04:07.280 --> 04:11.240
Being here, I feel like I'm in a skin
that doesn't belong to me.

04:12.040 --> 04:12.960
It's uncomfortable.

04:17.200 --> 04:19.720
-Now you've got so many demon hunters
-This is for you.

04:19.800 --> 04:20.800
following you.

04:21.839 --> 04:25.160
Maybe you don't really need me anymore.

04:36.080 --> 04:37.160
I need to talk to you.

04:37.240 --> 04:40.120
Commander Li wants to see me.
Let's talk later.

05:23.720 --> 05:24.760
So,

05:25.840 --> 05:27.640
I'm leaving, Wu Shiguang.

05:32.960 --> 05:34.600
You idiot weasel.

05:59.200 --> 06:01.760
Formless Moon, hear my command.

06:05.960 --> 06:06.880
Go.

06:08.000 --> 06:09.760
Activate the Nuwa Formation

06:10.760 --> 06:13.120
and reveal the Four Pillars

06:13.960 --> 06:15.160
that uphold the earth.

06:15.760 --> 06:16.680
Yes.

06:38.680 --> 06:39.520
Have you seen You Chi?

06:48.320 --> 06:49.800
-Wangyan!
-Canyue.

06:52.000 --> 06:53.000
Canyue!

06:54.000 --> 06:54.840
Canyue.

06:56.960 --> 06:58.040
Stop her.

07:00.040 --> 07:01.000
Canyue.

07:16.400 --> 07:17.280
Wangyan,

07:18.960 --> 07:20.480
what happened?

07:22.240 --> 07:23.320
Jiu Ying…

07:29.000 --> 07:30.640
Jiu Ying isn't dead.

07:35.880 --> 07:37.840
He possessed Wuyi.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.880
Do you remember

07:46.960 --> 07:49.920
the four divine trees that uphold
the earth I told you about?

07:50.000 --> 07:52.160
The Tree of Water grew beneath the sea.

07:52.240 --> 07:55.640
Its trunk is now the throne
in Formless Moon's main hall.

07:59.960 --> 08:00.880
Go.

08:01.520 --> 08:02.440
Yes.

08:06.080 --> 08:10.120
The Crying Elm,
now reduced to a broken stump,

08:10.200 --> 08:12.200
is the Tree of Earth.

08:24.640 --> 08:27.240
The Firefluff Tree hidden in the axle
of Wei mansion's weaving workshop

08:27.320 --> 08:28.160
is the Tree of Fire.

08:41.240 --> 08:44.200
Why does Jiu Ying want to destroy
the Four Pillars?

08:44.960 --> 08:46.640
He wants the earth to collapse,

08:46.720 --> 08:48.400
all living things to perish,

08:49.120 --> 08:50.560
and this world

08:51.560 --> 08:53.960
to be left with nothing
but fear and despair.

08:55.080 --> 08:56.680
Where is the Tree of Metal?

09:00.120 --> 09:02.240
The Shilin Sect's Golden Scale Tree

09:04.040 --> 09:05.080
is the Tree of Metal.

09:06.320 --> 09:07.160
Good thing

09:07.240 --> 09:10.000
there is the Eternal Formation
keeping them away.

09:10.720 --> 09:11.560
No.

09:14.240 --> 09:15.240
Wuyi

09:16.680 --> 09:18.040
has a Shilin Sect token.

09:19.360 --> 09:21.800
TOKEN OF SCALES

09:50.520 --> 09:52.240
Wu Shiguang, why haven't
you come to find me?

09:53.600 --> 09:56.520
If you don't show up today,
I won't be so easy

09:57.240 --> 09:58.280
to cheer up!

10:12.400 --> 10:13.440
Ye Changsheng,

10:13.960 --> 10:16.840
bring the nearby townsfolk
into the Shilin Sect for protection.

10:16.920 --> 10:17.760
Yes.

10:20.280 --> 10:21.120
Hurry!

10:22.280 --> 10:23.440
Watch your step!

10:26.760 --> 10:28.440
This way! Quick!

10:31.360 --> 10:32.240
Keep up!

10:35.840 --> 10:37.760
-Be careful! Hurry!
-Go!

10:38.440 --> 10:39.480
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

10:40.400 --> 10:41.240
Move!

10:41.320 --> 10:42.000
-Go!
-Keep up!

10:42.080 --> 10:43.320
Inside! Go!

10:53.240 --> 10:55.320
If the Four Pillars collapse completely,

10:56.920 --> 11:00.640
heaven and earth,
including the Shilin Sect, will topple.

11:00.720 --> 11:02.120
We have to stop Jiu Ying,

11:02.960 --> 11:03.800
but…

11:05.800 --> 11:06.920
Master Dragon Deity.

11:24.640 --> 11:27.080
My soul I devote. Long live the dragon.

11:34.520 --> 11:37.200
Master Dragon Deity, we await your orders.

11:45.000 --> 11:46.240
Members of the Formless Moon

11:46.320 --> 11:48.560
can draw on the elemental power
of the Four Pillars.

11:49.080 --> 11:52.400
The possessed sisters
will be much stronger and hard to defeat.

11:53.640 --> 11:56.280
Only spells that counter
the pillars' elements

11:56.360 --> 11:57.280
can oppose them.

11:58.040 --> 12:00.800
Mo Yuntan, your artifact,
the Spirit Brush,

12:00.880 --> 12:03.160
uses ink-based water magic.

12:03.680 --> 12:04.520
It can counter fire.

12:06.560 --> 12:07.840
Leave the Firefluff Tree to me.

12:13.720 --> 12:16.120
The Crying Elm is the oldest tree,

12:17.040 --> 12:18.000
the ancestor of all trees.

12:39.320 --> 12:42.920
My artifact, Golden Resonance,
counters wood. Perfect.

12:51.000 --> 12:53.480
My blade is a divine weapon
left behind by a mountain demon.

12:53.560 --> 12:55.280
For centuries, it'd drawn

12:55.360 --> 12:57.600
on the essence of the soil
from the peak of Mount Nandang.

12:57.680 --> 12:58.520
Earth counters water.

12:58.600 --> 13:00.560
I'll handle the Formless Moon's
Tree of Water.

13:08.560 --> 13:10.280
That leaves the Golden Scale Tree.

13:12.360 --> 13:13.240
Hua Qi…

14:10.080 --> 14:13.400
What, are you going to attack your sister?

14:14.280 --> 14:16.680
It's Jiu Ying I'm going to strike at.

14:17.920 --> 14:19.480
Give my sister back!

14:54.840 --> 14:55.680
What happened?

14:57.560 --> 14:58.520
You Chi,

14:59.760 --> 15:01.760
-leave.
-No way.

15:01.840 --> 15:03.480
How can I leave when you're like this?

15:04.080 --> 15:06.160
Hua Qi, I'm no healer.

15:06.240 --> 15:07.520
Is there any way I can help?

15:08.200 --> 15:09.160
Yes.

15:09.240 --> 15:10.480
Take my place

15:11.280 --> 15:12.560
and save the Golden Scale Tree.

15:13.680 --> 15:15.200
Save the Golden Scale Tree?

15:15.280 --> 15:16.520
How?

15:17.240 --> 15:19.360
Should I catch bugs or water it?

15:36.800 --> 15:39.200
Always keep this token on you.

15:39.280 --> 15:42.520
Otherwise, the ancient formations
all over the Shilin Sect

15:42.600 --> 15:45.040
will reduce you to ashes in an instant.

15:52.000 --> 15:53.000
Remember.

15:53.920 --> 15:56.920
No matter what you are
or how capable you are,

15:58.000 --> 16:01.480
always give it everything you've got,
and do your best.

16:02.440 --> 16:04.080
Only then can you have no regrets.

16:13.200 --> 16:17.040
A little weasel thinks
he can fight a nine-tailed fox?

16:21.440 --> 16:22.520
Haven't you heard?

16:23.920 --> 16:25.160
Fire counters metal.

16:26.160 --> 16:27.440
Hua Qi,

16:28.640 --> 16:30.720
you're draining your power.

16:30.800 --> 16:33.160
Almost done, Master Dragon Deity.

16:34.280 --> 16:35.440
Hold on a little longer.

16:46.000 --> 16:47.280
Wangyan!

16:54.960 --> 16:56.320
Wangyan,

16:57.320 --> 17:01.040
did you think I couldn't beat you?

17:50.080 --> 17:50.960
Shiguang.

17:52.000 --> 17:55.200
You are the only one in this world
I still can't let go of.

17:55.840 --> 17:57.280
Though I am gone,

17:57.800 --> 17:59.360
the Star Stone remains.

18:00.040 --> 18:01.400
If you find yourself
in dire straits one day,

18:02.000 --> 18:03.640
it may yet help you once.

18:04.520 --> 18:05.720
But remember this.

18:06.360 --> 18:08.200
The Star Stone's power is too great.

18:08.920 --> 18:09.960
Do not use it rashly.

18:10.040 --> 18:11.000
Master…

18:12.320 --> 18:13.400
"Heaven and earth tremble.

18:13.480 --> 18:15.080
Chaos fills the world.

18:15.160 --> 18:16.680
An old soul returns against time.

18:17.200 --> 18:19.240
A new moon reshapes the world."

18:19.320 --> 18:20.640
"Heaven and earth tremble.

18:21.720 --> 18:22.840
Chaos fills the world."

18:23.880 --> 18:26.280
The last share
of Chi Wen's Dragon Deity's Power

18:26.960 --> 18:28.240
took Ji Ling's heart stone

18:28.320 --> 18:30.200
to the Dragon Abyss.

18:31.000 --> 18:32.680
Perhaps thousands of years from now,

18:33.200 --> 18:34.600
it may take human form.

18:35.600 --> 18:37.040
"An old soul returns against time."

18:39.400 --> 18:40.400
"An old soul returns against time."

18:40.920 --> 18:41.960
Hua Qi.

18:44.880 --> 18:45.960
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

18:51.200 --> 18:52.280
Give me your hand.

18:56.440 --> 18:57.440
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

18:57.520 --> 18:59.880
Use my blood to activate
the Star Stone illusion

19:00.480 --> 19:02.880
and bring Ji Ling's heart stone inside.

19:03.400 --> 19:04.600
Go, now.

19:04.680 --> 19:05.760
All right.

19:28.240 --> 19:29.280
This…

19:29.880 --> 19:31.480
isn't my limit yet.

19:38.800 --> 19:40.440
Do my best

19:42.000 --> 19:43.400
and leave no regrets!

19:48.000 --> 19:49.640
You only know fire counters metal.

19:50.640 --> 19:54.080
But do you know that ice counters fire?

21:25.000 --> 21:26.400
A fleeting moment in the mortal world

21:26.920 --> 21:28.280
is a thousand years in the illusion.

21:28.800 --> 21:32.520
Master Dragon Deity,
I will bring Ji Ling back.

21:42.440 --> 21:45.720
Your weapon's gone,
and you still won't give up?

21:45.800 --> 21:47.000
The blade's gone,

21:48.440 --> 21:49.560
but I'm still here.

21:49.640 --> 21:51.920
Today, I am going to defeat you!

22:05.640 --> 22:06.640
Who says

22:07.520 --> 22:08.680
a weasel

22:09.520 --> 22:10.880
can't beat a nine-tailed fox?

22:24.920 --> 22:25.960
Wu Shiguang,

22:28.040 --> 22:28.960
this time,

22:31.120 --> 22:33.080
I… I didn't

22:35.000 --> 22:36.200
hold you back.

22:44.680 --> 22:45.800
You'd better not

22:47.200 --> 22:50.200
lock me inside the Cosmic Pouch again.

25:20.120 --> 25:21.160
"An old soul…"

25:23.760 --> 25:25.080
THE OLD DRAGON FALLS
THE NEW DRAGON RISES

25:25.160 --> 25:26.280
"Returns against time."

25:29.880 --> 25:30.720
You're back.

25:31.800 --> 25:32.920
I am.

25:34.400 --> 25:35.280
And

25:36.920 --> 25:38.240
so are they.

26:01.760 --> 26:02.760
Master.

26:23.040 --> 26:24.440
Why are you all back?

26:24.960 --> 26:27.440
Because Ji Ling has already
awakened the people

26:27.960 --> 26:29.040
of the Formless Moon.

26:31.000 --> 26:32.160
Wake.

28:27.240 --> 28:28.280
Wang,

28:29.320 --> 28:33.040
the Four Pillars have been corrupted
by the evil energy inside Jiu Ying.

28:34.560 --> 28:37.520
Only by sacrificing
the Formless Moon power within us

28:38.240 --> 28:40.440
can we cleanse that evil energy.

28:41.120 --> 28:43.120
The wrong was ours.

28:43.960 --> 28:46.080
Let us make amends ourselves.

28:46.680 --> 28:50.080
Wang, we leave the rest to you.

28:50.840 --> 28:52.000
Save this world

28:52.520 --> 28:54.760
we have guarded for a millennium.

28:59.000 --> 28:59.920
What is it?

29:01.000 --> 29:02.360
What did the Moon Summoning Pearl say?

29:03.560 --> 29:04.520
Nothing.

29:05.160 --> 29:07.360
The sisters have all come to their senses.

29:09.280 --> 29:10.840
They're repairing the Four Pillars.

29:14.680 --> 29:16.120
The collapse has stopped.

29:17.480 --> 29:19.720
Looks like they're all restored.

29:53.080 --> 29:54.160
I'll check on the Golden Scale Tree.

29:54.240 --> 29:55.760
Be careful.

29:56.480 --> 29:57.320
I've got it covered here.

30:23.440 --> 30:25.760
You're still alive?

30:26.280 --> 30:29.560
Too bad Lu Wuyi thought
you were truly dead.

30:29.640 --> 30:31.200
She was so heartbroken

30:32.120 --> 30:35.080
that even her soul scattered into nothing.

30:36.160 --> 30:37.120
Jiu Ying,

30:38.160 --> 30:39.600
you killed Wu.

30:41.320 --> 30:42.320
Today,

30:43.080 --> 30:45.520
I will make sure
your soul is utterly destroyed.

30:59.280 --> 31:00.320
Lu Wuyi,

31:01.560 --> 31:03.680
you woke up again?

31:03.760 --> 31:04.960
I told you,

31:06.520 --> 31:08.120
the one who should get out

31:09.360 --> 31:10.680
is you.

31:14.080 --> 31:14.960
Wu.

31:18.640 --> 31:19.600
Ji,

31:20.960 --> 31:23.440
Jiu Ying has been trying to take control.

31:24.640 --> 31:25.600
Ji,

31:26.680 --> 31:27.640
do it.

31:28.720 --> 31:29.920
Kill me.

31:35.120 --> 31:37.480
Since I was created, I've been controlled

31:38.440 --> 31:39.640
my whole life.

31:41.840 --> 31:43.200
This time,

31:44.960 --> 31:47.200
I want to be my true self.

31:49.640 --> 31:50.760
Help me,

31:52.320 --> 31:53.400
Ji.

32:09.480 --> 32:10.320
Form up.

32:13.400 --> 32:14.240
Qisha of the Southern Dipper.

32:14.320 --> 32:15.320
Tiantong of the Southern Dipper.

32:15.400 --> 32:16.440
Pojun of the Northern Dipper.

32:16.520 --> 32:17.400
In positions!

34:39.520 --> 34:40.360
Master.

35:05.320 --> 35:06.240
You Chi.

35:06.920 --> 35:07.880
Wangyan,

35:08.480 --> 35:09.520
I did great

35:10.880 --> 35:12.080
this time.

35:14.160 --> 35:15.320
She said

35:15.400 --> 35:16.800
a weasel

35:17.720 --> 35:19.080
couldn't beat a nine-tailed fox,

35:19.600 --> 35:21.760
but look,

35:23.320 --> 35:24.880
I still beat her.

35:29.520 --> 35:31.560
I helped, didn't I?

35:32.080 --> 35:33.160
Oh, right.

35:33.720 --> 35:34.680
Look.

35:35.360 --> 35:36.280
I was

35:37.880 --> 35:39.480
so smart this time.

35:41.760 --> 35:43.000
Wu Shiguang

35:43.080 --> 35:45.480
won't get to call me an idiot again.

35:46.920 --> 35:48.040
Do you know?

35:48.640 --> 35:50.800
Wu Shiguang always says

35:51.400 --> 35:53.120
that when danger comes,

35:54.840 --> 35:57.200
I'm the type to dig a hole and hide in it.

35:57.280 --> 35:59.200
Before you came,

35:59.960 --> 36:01.600
I was so sad,

36:02.720 --> 36:05.200
because I was going to die here alone,

36:06.680 --> 36:08.120
and no one would ever know.

36:09.640 --> 36:10.800
Wu Shiguang

36:11.640 --> 36:13.720
must think I ran away again.

36:17.160 --> 36:18.400
Oh, right.

36:19.000 --> 36:20.880
Remember to tell him

36:21.440 --> 36:22.600
that I…

36:24.000 --> 36:25.160
I really…

36:27.120 --> 36:30.400
really did my best. I did…

36:31.840 --> 36:33.560
I did my best.

36:37.240 --> 36:39.200
You Chi. You Chi!

38:21.400 --> 38:22.320
How?

38:23.040 --> 38:25.640
Lu Wuyi's soul was unusually resilient.

38:26.160 --> 38:28.640
I was never able to find a way
to erase it completely.

38:29.240 --> 38:31.680
I should thank you, Wu Shiguang.

38:31.760 --> 38:33.920
With your Dragon Deity's Power,

38:34.440 --> 38:37.240
you wiped out the last trace of her soul

38:37.760 --> 38:40.640
and let me own this body completely.

38:44.080 --> 38:46.560
Why won't Lu Wuyi's body die?

38:49.400 --> 38:50.680
HEAVEN AND EARTH TREMBLE
CHAOS FILLS THE WORLD

38:50.760 --> 38:52.040
AN OLD SOUL RETURNS AGAINST TIME
A NEW MOON RESHAPES THE WORLD

38:54.080 --> 38:55.520
The Oracle Stone is missing a piece.

38:55.600 --> 38:57.080
The Oracle Stone!

38:57.160 --> 39:00.240
Besides a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit,

39:00.960 --> 39:03.040
a fragment of the Oracle Stone
is in her too.

39:05.120 --> 39:06.480
Wu's body

39:06.560 --> 39:09.520
was made from the flesh
and blood of nine-tailed foxes.

39:09.600 --> 39:13.040
It has the power of rebirth
granted by the Formless Moon.

39:13.760 --> 39:17.040
If she also has the Oracle Stone's
ever-living divine power,

39:18.200 --> 39:19.080
then…

39:24.200 --> 39:25.960
Is there really no other way?

39:28.480 --> 39:30.120
"An old soul returns against time.

39:31.680 --> 39:33.360
A new moon reshapes the world."

39:37.000 --> 39:38.000
A new moon…

39:49.720 --> 39:51.320
There is still one way.

39:53.840 --> 39:55.280
And it's the only way.

39:59.000 --> 40:00.320
You've thought of it too.

40:01.640 --> 40:02.880
What is it?

40:05.800 --> 40:07.280
Turn back time

40:07.840 --> 40:09.240
and go back to the past

40:10.920 --> 40:13.120
to stop Lu Wuyi from ever being born.

40:13.840 --> 40:14.920
In other words,

40:16.440 --> 40:18.840
erase Lu Wuyi's existence completely.

40:24.680 --> 40:26.640
Didn't Lonescale tell you?

40:27.680 --> 40:30.640
The recent past of a few days
can be changed.

40:31.760 --> 40:34.320
But Lu Wuyi was born 50 years ago.

40:35.280 --> 40:39.480
To go back that far and change the past?

40:41.320 --> 40:42.760
A fool's dream.

40:44.680 --> 40:46.200
"A new moon reshapes the world."

40:46.720 --> 40:50.160
Since the Oracle Stone
gave such a prophecy,

40:50.960 --> 40:52.360
it means

40:55.040 --> 40:56.840
this is destined to happen.

40:59.840 --> 41:01.800
I was a fallen star
from beyond the heavens.

41:02.960 --> 41:04.920
I'm not bound by the laws of this world.

41:08.560 --> 41:10.200
There was one question

41:11.000 --> 41:12.760
I spent my whole life pondering.

41:13.760 --> 41:17.480
Even after bitter years of cultivation,
I could never solve it.

41:18.280 --> 41:20.680
You bear extraordinary power
from beyond the heavens.

41:20.760 --> 41:23.960
Slaughter is not your only choice.

41:24.560 --> 41:26.400
I hope that one day,

41:26.480 --> 41:28.840
you'll find the true meaning
of coming to this world

41:28.920 --> 41:30.880
after crossing

41:31.400 --> 41:32.720
countless galaxies.

41:33.800 --> 41:36.040
For the past thousand years,
I have asked myself

41:38.040 --> 41:40.720
why I came to this world

41:41.800 --> 41:42.840
and what

41:44.880 --> 41:46.800
I could do for it.

41:48.280 --> 41:49.720
Now I understand.

41:51.640 --> 41:55.160
After I crossed the galaxies
and came to this world,

41:56.280 --> 41:57.680
I brought disaster upon it

41:58.280 --> 41:59.960
and gave rise to Jiu Ying.

42:04.120 --> 42:05.160
So,

42:06.720 --> 42:08.920
it should be me who brings him to an end

42:10.160 --> 42:11.920
and saves this world.
